        "text" : "When greeting someone of the same gender, either engage in a handshake or greet with your hand over your heart. Shake hands with a looser grip than you would in the U.S. Be prepared for your counterpart to hold your hand longer than you're used to, perhaps for the entire course of small talk. ",
